name: Memories
description: This is a scan of a page in my sketchbook. Dated 9-1 and created in memory of the World Trade Center attacks. Now that the towers are gone all we have are postcards to remember them by. I was stuck in Europe when 9-11 happened. When I finally returned to the USA I couldn't find a postcard after the attacks so I drew one in my sketchbook. Created by Nite Owl, 2021 for the 20 year memoriam. 3600 x 4800 png. @naitooru (Twitter) @naito_oru (IG)
